python - <<'PY'
import json, subprocess, textwrap, re
repo='BillChirico/bills-bot'
pr=74

def run(cmd):
    return subprocess.check_output(cmd, text=True)

# Get current head sha
pr_data=json.loads(run(['gh','api',f'repos/{repo}/pulls/{pr}']))
head_sha=pr_data['head']['sha']

# paginate review threads
unresolved=[]
cursor=None
while True:
    q='''query($owner:String!, $name:String!, $number:Int!, $after:String){\n  repository(owner:$owner, name:$name){\n    pullRequest(number:$number){\n      reviewThreads(first:100, after:$after){\n        pageInfo{hasNextPage endCursor}\n        nodes{\n          id\n          isResolved\n          isOutdated\n          path\n          line\n          originalLine\n          comments(first:20){\n            nodes{body author{login} createdAt url}\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}'''
    vars={'owner':'BillChirico','name':'bills-bot','number':pr,'after':cursor}
    out=run(['gh','api','graphql','-f',f'query={q}','-f',f'owner={vars["owner"]}','-f',f'name={vars["name"]}','-F',f'number={vars["number"]}'] + (['-f',f'after={cursor}'] if cursor else []))
    data=json.loads(out)['data']['repository']['pullRequest']['reviewThreads']
    for t in data['nodes']:
        if not t['isResolved']:
            comments=t.get('comments',{}).get('nodes',[])
            summary=''
            if comments:
                summary=(comments[-1].get('body') or comments[0].get('body') or '').strip().replace('\n',' ')
            unresolved.append({
                'id': t['id'],
                'path': t.get('path'),
                'line': t.get('line') or t.get('originalLine'),
                'isOutdated': t.get('isOutdated'),
                'summary': summary[:300]
            })
    if not data['pageInfo']['hasNextPage']:
        break
    cursor=data['pageInfo']['endCursor']

# top-level reviews
reviews=json.loads(run(['gh','api',f'repos/{repo}/pulls/{pr}/reviews','--paginate']))
if isinstance(reviews, dict):
    reviews=[reviews]
actionable=[]
non_actionable_pattern=re.compile(r'^(lgtm!?|looks good!?|nice work!?|great work!?|approved!?|ship it!?|thanks!?|thank you!?)[.!\s]*$', re.I)
for r in reviews:
    state=r.get('state')
    body=(r.get('body') or '').strip()
    if state not in ('CHANGES_REQUESTED','COMMENTED'):
        continue
    if not body:
        continue
    # actionable heuristic
    if non_actionable_pattern.match(body):
        continue
    # only if no new commits after this review
    if r.get('commit_id') != head_sha:
        continue
    actionable.append({
        'id': r.get('id'),
        'state': state,
        'user': (r.get('user') or {}).get('login'),
        'commit_id': r.get('commit_id'),
        'submitted_at': r.get('submitted_at'),
        'body': body[:1200]
    })

print(json.dumps({'pr':pr,'head_sha':head_sha,'unresolved_threads':unresolved,'actionable_high_level_reviews':actionable}, indent=2))
PY
